    <br>
    <sup>─x</sup>&frasl;<sub>─1</sub> ≤ <sup>12</sup>&frasl;<sub>─1</sub> ; When dividing by negative (─), the inequality sign will change
    <br>
    <strong>x ≥ −12</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
