    <br>
  ─3x   ≤ ─ 15 divide both sides by ─3
  <br>
  <sup>─3x</sup>&frasl;<sub>─3</sub ≤ <sup>─15</sup>&frasl;<sub>─3</sub> ; When dividing by negative (-), the inequality sign will change
  <br>
   <strong>x   ≥ 5</strong>
